<p>The speed at which CLO rated debt is paid down after the reinvestment end date depends on several factors, including the behavior of the CLO manager, market condtions, the post-reinvestment end date language of the CLO (coverage tests, WARF tests, CCC limits, WAL tests, asset maturity criteria, etc.), and the composition of the collateral pool&#8230;. </p>
